{"tid":659817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[堪比單程證150] 每日平均112人! 香港近１０年吸４０萬「外地專才」!","createTime":"2018-05-10T07:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T15:22:48.000Z","uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d8d52162ab37cd3327958f0f7a503b5a0e542f","tid":659817,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"10/05/2018 09:58<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社１０日專訊》據政府向立法會提交的文件顯示，本港由２００８年至今年３月，通過<span style=\"color: red;\">「一般就業政策」、「輸入內地人才計劃」及「優秀人才入境計劃」</span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引入逾４０﹒７萬名外地專才</span></span></strong>，當中３個計劃的引入人數佔比分別約為７７％、２２％及１％。<br />\n<br />\n　　文件顯示，「輸入內地人才計劃」的獲批人數，去年按年升１９％至１﹒２４萬人，創出新高，引入的人才中，主要來自「學術研究及教育」、「建築╱測量」及「金融服務」行業，約十年間分別有２﹒６２萬、２﹒２萬和１﹒２３萬人；而資訊科技業的專才則只有２７９０人，每年平均不到３００人。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於透過「優秀人才入境計劃」引人的人才，去年數字按年升５０﹒６％至４１１人，為２００９年以來最高。若單計去年的數字，當中大部分來自「金融及會計服務」及「資訊科技╱電訊」業，分別有１１４和７６人、佔整體約２７﹒７％及１８﹒５％。（ｄｌ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280510516&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN280510516%26page%3D1%26category%3Dlatest&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6Ghxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7d077fff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280510516&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest</a>"},{"pid":"b9a0d6d9decd967a8f4fefb94389a35c6408b77e","tid":659817,"uid":53060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1Bf25ehApkPiZ_3jNpYmCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/5e6455c8d4f04fc1b7706b82a8aad33e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1Bf25ehApkPiZ_3jNpYmCA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c